VDR Plugin 'admin' Revision History
-----------------------------------

2008-04-09: Version 0.8.0
 
- Switch from i18n to gettext for vdr-1.5.x


2008-01-08: Version 0.7.5
 
- Added 2 Parameters (--oldstyle, --idx2def)
  For different handling of List Elements ( see README )
  and backwards compatibility (use --oldstyle for pre 0.7.0 behaviour)


2008-01-03: Version 0.7.4
 
- Added Italian translation ( Thanks to Diego )


2007-12-11: Version 0.7.3
 
- Another Bugfix ( Thanks to RalfW )


2007-12-01: Version 0.7.2
 
- Bugfix for selecting last list item ( Thanks to OnTecNo )


2007-11-21: Version 0.7.1
 
- Bugfix


2007-11-21: Version 0.7.0
 
- Changed handling of Lists ( using Value instead if index )
  To convert an old admin.conf to a new just start setsdmconf.sh
- All Scripts adapted to Gen2VDR 2.0  


2007-03-10: Version 0.6.2
 
- Bugfix preventing a crash when new String is longer than old one.


2007-01-18: Version 0.6.1

- Added Keys for saving and restarting
- several internal changes.


2007-01-09: Version 0.6.0

- Minor bugfixes
- Added new Variable Type F for non-editable Fields
- New values for choices (a-z,A-Z,0-9,-f,-d,-F,-D)
- Major changes in gentoo scripts


2006-12-28: Version 0.5.1

- Fixed a bug when value is an empty string ( reported by UweS )


2006-04-30: Version 0.5.0

- Now the admin.sh script will be executed with these parameter:
   -init  : During initialization ( vdr startup )
   -start : When opening the Admin Menu
   -save  : After saving the changes in the menu
- Changes for vdr Version 1.4.0 ( won't work with an older version )
- removed parameter for config directory
- added a title for submenues
  (suggested by Ronny Kornexl)


2006-03-07: Version 0.4.1

- No longer writing leading blanks for numeric values
- Updated Gentoo scripts

  
2005-12-07: Version 0.4.0

- Added option to create a Mainmenu entry
  (suggested by Ronny Kornexl)


2005-11-24: Version 0.3.3

- Added Navigation via numbers on first menu page.
  (suggested by Ronny Kornexl)


2005-11-11: Version 0.3.2

- Added init script setadmin.sh


2005-10-05: Version 0.3.1

- Added support for internationalization.
  (suggested by Ronny Kornexl)


2005-02-25: Version 0.3.0

- Default for directory of config files changed to plugins/admin
- Adding script cfgvar.sh for writing variables to /etc/conf.d/vdr


2005-01-18: Version 0.2.4

- Parameter -d for directory of config files implemented


2004-11-03: Version 0.2.3

- Minor fixes for Gentoo scripting


2004-10-21: Version 0.2.2

- Updated scripts and renamed scriptpath to gentoo instead of scripts.


2004-08-12: Version 0.2.0

- Added Submenues and comment lines.


2004-02-25: Version 0.1.0

- Initial revision.
